<div class="row">

  <div class="col-sm-12">
    <blockquote>
      <p>Do poprawnej rejestracji zgłoszenia będziesz potrzebował(-a) dołączyć następujące dokumenty (w formacie PDF):<br>
      <li>Potwierdzenie dokonania wpłaty: w tytule przelewu wpłaty powinno być „za egzamin i wydanie świadectwa amatorskiego”<br>       
        Urząd Komunikacji Elektronicznej<br>
        ul. Giełdowa 7/9<br>
        01-211 Warszawa<br>
        Nr konta: 75 1010 1010 0060 4422 3100 0000<br>
      </li>
      <li>W przypadku osób niepełnoletnich skan pisemnej zgody opiekuna prawnego na przystąpienie do egzaminu.</li>
      </p>
    </blockquote>
  </div> <!-- /.col-sm-5 -->

  <div class="col-sm-12">

    <%= f.hidden_field :creator_id %>

    <fieldset class="my-fieldset">
      <legend class="my-fieldset"><%= t('.fieldset_title') %></legend>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="form-group required col-sm-4">
          <%= f.label :email, class: 'control-label' %>
          <%= f.text_field :email, autofocus: false, class: 'form-control input-sm', disabled: false, readonly: true %>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group required col-sm-4">
          <%= f.label :name, class: 'control-label' %>
          <%= f.text_field :name, autofocus: false, class: 'form-control input-sm', disabled: false, readonly: true %>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group required col-sm-4">
          <%= f.label :given_names, class: 'control-label' %>
          <%= f.text_field :given_names, autofocus: false, class: 'form-control input-sm', disabled: false, readonly: true %>
        </div>
      </div> <!--/row -->

      <div class="row">
        <div class="form-group col-sm-4">
          <%= f.label :pesel, class: 'control-label' %>
          <%= f.text_field :pesel, autofocus: current_user.pesel.blank?, 
                  class: 'form-control input-sm',
                  disabled: false, readonly: current_user.pesel.present? %>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group required col-sm-5">
          <%= f.label :citizenship_code, class: 'control-label' %>
          <%= f.country_select :citizenship_code, priority_countries = ["pl"], options = {}, autofocus: current_user.pesel.present?, :class => "form-control input-sm" %>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group col-sm-3">
          <%= f.label :phone, class: 'control-label' %>
          <%= f.text_field :phone, class: 'form-control input-sm', disabled: false %>
        </div>
      </div> <!--/row -->

      <div class="row">
        <div class="form-group required col-sm-4">
          <%= f.label :birth_place, class: 'control-label' %>
          <%= f.text_field :birth_place, class: 'form-control input-sm', disabled: false %>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group required col-sm-4">
          <%= f.label :birth_date, class: 'control-label' %>
          <%= f.text_field :birth_date, class: 'form-control input-sm datepicker', disabled: false %>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group required col-sm-4">
          <%= f.label :family_name, class: 'control-label' %>
          <%= f.text_field :family_name, class: 'form-control input-sm', disabled: false %>
        </div>
      </div> <!--/row -->


    </fieldset>

  </div> <!--/col-sm-12 -->
</div> <!--/row -->
